{"tid":1914091,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"試著說「五大目標，缺一不可」","createTime":"2020-03-07T09:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T15:34:37.000Z","uid":23094,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4aeacfdbb337847fc81726eab2ead4534f8c001f","tid":1914091,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"「訴求」係你對對方仲有期望，幻想<br />\n希望得到佢嘅可憐、施捨<br />\n求佢畀你想得到嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n但係今時今日你仲會唔會咁諗？<br />\n適逢梁義士嘅生忌<br />\n大家係時候改變一下心態<br />\n<br />\n「目標」係靠自己爭取<br />\n唔需要乞求人<br />\n唔到其他人話批唔批準<br />\n想要嘅嘢就要得到手<br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大目標，缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大目標 缺一不可<br />\n沒有普選 唯有獨立<br />\n加入工會 全民三罷</span></span>"},{"pid":"711ac1f9948c659363b4f43a3441390db8adaac2","tid":1914091,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:42:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大目標，缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3796e2c17ffdb72bb61bdeaa3b9ec4efabd98197","tid":1914091,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"我想揾五大狗閪"},{"pid":"f4a3b3a34b48ab9175d2993ea7cbcc8b2e1fca70","tid":1914091,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"159ade32608b816a74ed632fc35d116bf56b30df","tid":1914091,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c1a71a95dd3c9818fec5841703c5de950f2e196","tid":1914091,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"傻閪樓主 拉"},{"pid":"1f978742fdb8441ec5abc2a38d55ffdf2f06efe2","tid":1914091,"uid":23094,"like":0,"